NAME: Uranius Mons
Additional_Info: Name introduced to represent the entire edifice. See the entry for Uranius Patera.

NAME: Uranius Patera
Additional_Info: Size changed Sept. 19, 2007 to correspond only to the central depression.

NAME: Utopia Rupes
Origin: Named for calssical albedo feature at 55N, 260W.
Additional_Info: Changed from Utopia Rupes to Utopia Rupēs August 27, 2013.

NAME: Vaduz
Origin: Capital of the Principality of Liechtenstein.

NAME: Valles Marineris
Origin: General name of the system of canyons honoring the scientific team of the Mariner 9 program.

NAME: Varus Valles
Origin: Classical name for present Var River, France.

NAME: Victoria
Origin: Town in the Republic of Seychelles.

NAME: Vistula Valles
Origin: Classical name for modern Wistla River in Poland.

NAME: Voeykov
Origin: A. I.. Russian climatologist and geographer (1842-1916).

NAME: Vulcani Pelagus
Origin: Named for Vulcan, Roman god of fire.

NAME: Weert
Origin: Town in the Netherlands. (Spelling corrected from Weer.)

NAME: Wum
Origin: Town in Cameroon. Name dropped because crater cannot be located on imagery.

NAME: Yaonis Regio
Origin: Named for Chinese Emperor Yao. flood occurred during his reign.

NAME: Yellowknife
Origin: Town in the Northwest Territories, Canada.
